  "name": "RPlog_Dathomir_Raid",
  "title": "The Dathomir Raid",
  "summary": "A New Republic strike force ambushes the Imperial container depot at Dathomir, guarded by a CR90 and two carriers, with Captain Racknar's Nebulon-B frigates, Raxis 'Spider' L'ygr's Falcon Squadron, Lance 'Wildman' Corbet's Ghosts, and Marine boarding teams under Lt. Vengan Draelis alongside Twila's VSC mercenaries and Gren Delede's VigSec commandos. The raid is itself a trap sprung by Marshal Krieg Inrokana, who flies disguised in an unmarked TIE: as the rebels overwhelm the CR90 and storm its bridge and hangar, Krieg's full Task Force Inquisitor under Captain Keline Nelhrn jumps in with Interdictors and the looming HIMS Malevolence, sealing every escape but death or the planet. A desperate, lopsided slaughter follows; Captain Racknar's frigates charge to their deaths to buy time, Raxis is shot down by Krieg and Dante and crashes into Dathomir's swamps, and dozens of NR pilots die. The Imperials capture or destroy most of the fleet, though three damaged corvettes slingshot away, and Krieg dispatches shuttles to recover his stranded 501st troopers and hunt the downed rebels on the surface.",
